Endemic to the Upemba Swamps in Katanga, S 
<collectingCountry id="F34BF6959973FFC80BE6F43AF668F454" box="[2288,2437,3000,3029]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="56" pageNumber="671">DR Congo</collectingCountry>
